"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36030a5b2884be69c2f1a3cde18d69401d39458","tid":2305853,"uid":236171,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/30/131415_8a5fe96377c1066632b3a92f3ddb94b2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F30%2F131415_8a5fe96377c1066632b3a92f3ddb94b2.gif&h=44e2bb33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffa893e4d964d1082b0d72101aea1daaee1e266d","tid":2305853,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"邊有14億個黨員呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b9d26a4c50b5d07d4d0b29cba08755ad6a2b31","tid":2305853,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"咁sorry囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次唔問咁多嘢，直接叫你返轉頭ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1a3450b4d8c7cbd8f4d94c5b9b026c32eed98a","tid":2305853,"uid":363692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd30136e4057d3acdc9c6e20a551699e9db52f8d","tid":2305853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/realtime/2020/11/30/9165432.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Frealtime%2F2020%2F11%2F30%2F9165432.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=9f3a5f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陸媒報導，美國有關部門執法人員近期多次突擊檢查中國航運企業人員、航空公司機組人員的共產黨員身分，據統計，中國已有21艘輪船、16架次赴美航班遭到美方突擊盤查。報導引述中國權威消息人士稱，這是歧視性執法，意圖挑起意識形態對抗，中方將考慮採取對等反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n中國日報報導，近期，美國有關部門執法人員多次突擊檢查中方航運企業人員的共產黨員身分。截至11月11日，中方總計已有21艘輪船在美港口停靠時遭美突擊檢查；另9月以來，中方航空公司也有16架次赴美航班機組人員遭美方問詢、盤查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，美方在盤查中國人員過程，有時長達數個小時，且反覆「糾纏」共產黨員身分，連入黨原因也要盤問。<br />\n<br />\n報導並引述權威消息人士表示：「美方有關做法涉嫌歧視性執法，意圖挑起意識形態對抗，干擾中美正常人員往來，蓄意製造麻煩和障礙，讓人感到麥卡錫主義正在美復活。如美方執意對中共黨員持續滋擾甚至打壓迫害，中方將考慮採取對等反制措施。」<br />\n<br />\n早在今年7月17日，就有報導稱美國政府正考慮對所有中國共產黨員實施簽證限制。當時中國外交部發言人華春瑩表示，如果屬實，美方就是選擇公然與14億中國人民作對，公然站到世界五分之一人口的對立面。這完全違背中美兩國人民的意願和21世紀潮流，非常荒唐。<br />\n<br />\n報導刊出後，美國官方一直沒有出來澄清或是證實這項消息的真實性。直到近日傳出，中國已有多艘輪船及航班已遭到美方盤查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121474/5053992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121474%2F5053992&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=b2ef19b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121474/5053992</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"美國反制又俾人話😂😂"},{"pid":"b6f605d381341cff31fd884a17f51dc7bae28c87","tid":2305853,"uid":89869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"你哋美國人乜都唔使查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中國人全部都係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛國愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe95b4e2505643204212804dcd3c3b37c1d97a48","tid":2305853,"uid":38938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"查到係民主黨會唔會叫聲  同志好？"},{"pid":"f60dde3495460811cc89f86a467a3a8949cf1826","tid":2305853,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"美國依家仲敢唔敢誤炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />口交部咁惡"},{"pid":"499158d0b0d1804228bd08a55b4b903268fcbefa","tid":2305853,"uid":109726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f36030a5b2884be69c2f1a3cde18d69401d39458","tid":2305853,"uid":236171,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht